{"id": 2059, "genre": 1001, "title": "遇着啥事儿有可能让你删除/取关一个好友？", "description": "你会定期清理社交网络关注和通讯录联系人吗？清理好友/关注列表，你都有哪些依据和标准？", "record_count": 5117, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171212111104r1NqKOhSemTAyY8P.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-14T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 254208, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333612}, {"id": 254464, "content": "对别人说我的坏话，还不让别人告诉我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1074945}, {"id": 254720, "content": "撬我好友了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957988}, {"id": 254209, "content": "被欺骗……", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210019}, {"id": 254465, "content": "尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213665}, {"id": 254721, "content": "1.屏蔽理由百分之千是因为T刷屏，不管是鸡汤刷、自拍刷还是微商刷，每天连发五条以上，连发两天基本就蔽了。\n2.删除理由百分之千是因为讨厌T，或者太久不聊忘记是谁了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1189016}, {"id": 254210, "content": "发现他越来越丑，直到没话说", "image": "img/option/option/20171214140153J0bnLiaNdjtO1geY.jpg", "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763873}, {"id": 254466, "content": "说谎，背后阴招，三观不合，微商，一面之交，猎头，商户微信", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 254211, "content": "跟我前任在一起了还天天发合照?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205586}, {"id": 254212, "content": "天天发自拍的男性", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195368}, {"id": 254724, "content": "朋友圈里，你不赞我我不赞你，连点赞之交都当不了的联系人留来过年啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998837}, {"id": 254213, "content": "总是发那些不转就怎么怎么样的，或者是三观不合的，日常聊天尬聊那种，我可能会删了他或者让他躺在我好友列表的角落里", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205709}, {"id": 254469, "content": "不联系的人 然后朋友圈还屏蔽我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171773}, {"id": 254725, "content": "晾我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215367}, {"id": 255493, "content": "发蜈蚣给我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218474}, {"id": 254214, "content": "已经屏蔽我朋友圈且不说话的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212914}, {"id": 254215, "content": "分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212917}, {"id": 254216, "content": "很久不联系", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936791}, {"id": 254472, "content": "发现了更好看的人 于是取关了上一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775607}, {"id": 254217, "content": "我是销售。一般只有对方删我的我都不一定删留着说不定有用。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212938}, {"id": 254218, "content": "只能你帮她 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212945}, {"id": 254219, "content": "一直不聊天，且对方朋友圈价值也不高的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519556}, {"id": 254220, "content": "三观不合", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1150156}, {"id": 254732, "content": "加了我之后立马翻遍朋友圈，还点赞n年之前的朋友圈", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116613}, {"id": 254221, "content": "自顾自的发表三观，自顾自的认为你与她无法交流，自顾自的说着告别的话不再理你屏蔽你取关你。然而被屏蔽的本人更多的是被你指责性格缺陷，你所谓的对事不对人其实一直在苛责人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020052}, {"id": 254223, "content": "在现实中就觉得他是一个不值得在交往的朋友时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192231}, {"id": 254224, "content": "总是找我纠结一些很无聊的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076143}, {"id": 254225, "content": "ky行為和本能", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195079}, {"id": 254226, "content": "一直晒娃，一天八晒！除了她家娃哈也没有了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719364}, {"id": 257299, "content": "动态全是网图 网上的句子 ....加些?的emoji???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121755}, {"id": 254228, "content": "别人把我删了……但我觉得没啥对不起他的，我也很奇怪啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151475}, {"id": 254229, "content": "伤人还认为自己只是说话直率的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210637}, {"id": 254231, "content": "变成了田园女权，张口闭口直男癌。得，惹不起我躲不起么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746182}, {"id": 254487, "content": "就是 先加上后知道为人 再取决删或不删", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212496}, {"id": 254232, "content": "取关因为发各种广告", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212248}, {"id": 254233, "content": "那种被洗脑式的卖保险。每天发很多保险广告。本来还可以一起约饭，结果饭桌上都是推销，打电话问个事也是推销，而且不专业……拉黑，不见！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212869}, {"id": 257049, "content": "太喜欢又没可能的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1158050}, {"id": 254234, "content": "哈哈镜……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184453}, {"id": 254746, "content": "三观越来越不一致的票圈或转发评论……\n何苦争执，不如相忘江湖", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1215481}, {"id": 254235, "content": "哈哈哈\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184453}, {"id": 254747, "content": "除了经常联系的，其他都删除了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 254236, "content": "就是突然想删掉一些了", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146774}, {"id": 255516, "content": "没意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217378}, {"id": 258076, "content": "某天有事想联系对方，发现被删了，马勒戈壁，不删你留着过年么？删！而且永远不加！还有，发微信过去，装死不回，却发现他点赞了共同好友的朋友圈，删！不删你留着下蛋吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434643}, {"id": 258588, "content": "背后不是真人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1233850}, {"id": 254493, "content": "本来就不是朋友，只不过“留了个微信”，如果朋友圈发了我不想看的就直接屏蔽，只有发现已经删了我的我才会删了人家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213751}, {"id": 254238, "content": "毕业了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146774}, {"id": 254750, "content": "理所当然地向我索要帮助", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208026}, {"id": 254239, "content": "刷屏", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1211638}, {"id": 254240, "content": "天天在支付宝偷我的水，从来不给我浇水的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1209871}]}